{"tid":2270111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"十四五《建議》公佈 稱落實全面治權  政治先行 港恐「越管越死」","createTime":"2020-11-04T01:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T01:47:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0288757b21b5258446b6e53aac01d399a6c8985","tid":2270111,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201104/UZ7ECHOMGBHPVO5DZ6FAE4JJLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201104%2FUZ7ECHOMGBHPVO5DZ6FAE4JJLU%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcykPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=60cc9883\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201104%2FUZ7ECHOMGBHPVO5DZ6FAE4JJLU%2F&h=26dcac00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201104/UZ7ECHOMGBHPVO5DZ6FAE4JJLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n十四五《建議》公佈 稱落實全面治權 <br />\n政治先行 港恐「越管越死」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共中央昨公佈《關於制定第十四個五年規劃和2035年遠景目標的建議》（下稱《建議》）全文，當中提出要完善集中統一、高效權威的國家安全領導體制，落實中央對港澳特區的全面管治權，以及特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，堅決防範和遏制外部勢力干預港澳事務。有分析認為，中共以往視香港為「經濟城市」，但現在政治已蓋過經濟，香港勢將陷入中共「越控制就越死」的惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鮑彤轟五中全會一言堂 背離法治<br />\n<br />\n昨公佈的《建議》全文近兩萬字，按照程序國務院未來將根據《建議》制定關於「十四五」（2021-26）和2035年遠景目標的規。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。壞、顛覆、分裂活動。此外，要確保國家經濟安全，實現重要產業、基礎設施、戰略資源、重大科技等關鍵領域安全可控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kNIuzMsnxkna8HiGmgISXo9qDQ8=/3263x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C64KZZENNNDD5PSKPE5E3CTWRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkNIuzMsnxkna8HiGmgISXo9qDQ8%3D%2F3263x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC64KZZENNNDD5PSKPE5E3CTWRU.jpg&h=21ef2636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中共五中全會通過十四五規劃等建議。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n列國安重點 強調愛國精神<br />\n<br />\n《建議》把香港列為國家安全的重要一環，強調要維護憲法和《基本法》確定的特區憲制秩序，落實中央對特區全面管治權，落實特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，。。。。。。。。。。。。居民在內地發展政策措施。在兩岸問題上，《建議》支持符合條件的台資企業在大陸上市，支持福建探索海峽兩岸融合發展新路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QWgSf0LzPIdG_VbTlmiu2wH9-lI=/2244x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DLUPTHXJXNA5FBCING2RPJ54S4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQWgSf0LzPIdG_VbTlmiu2wH9-lI%3D%2F2244x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDLUPTHXJXNA5FBCING2RPJ54S4.jpg&h=5802e517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■十四五《建議》強調增強港人國家意識和愛國精神；圖為香港示威者戴習面具抗議。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂港抗爭聯外力 輻射大陸<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹對本報稱，與「十三五」（2016-20）規劃綱要比較，現在的「十四五」建議主要是從國家安全角度來看待香港，政治蓋過經濟部份。「香港本來可以免於政治干擾，但是中共很擔心大陸的政治鬥爭會透過香港與外部結合，然後輻射到大陸，影響習近平的政權穩定。所以中共要香港制定國安法，借外打內，但卻因此傷害了外國在港的利益，引發大風波。現在『十四五』把香港的政治部份同國際、國內的政治鬥爭連繫起來，提升至國家安全層面，將本來虛幻的危險變成實際危險。」<br />\n<br />\n「香港是中共覺得不安全的地方，但這種不安全是它自己造成。」劉銳紹指中共越覺得香港不安全便越要加強控制，但中共的國家安全體制損害了港人的民主自由，不受港人歡迎，「越控制就越死，陷入惡性循環。」"},{"pid":"e1a36190e371fdde88db57010c0a5226b9bc704e","tid":2270111,"uid":207767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"咁你廢左基本法腐乳佢啦，有咩用姐，唔用普通法，用哂支國憲法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d1accf5297fb78820b1ae4999b739cb3c896d4","tid":2270111,"uid":207767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"順便廢埋一國兩祭，直接將腥講加入支國政策規劃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa2c77ff3c2a1f08edc364d907104cad2f05ba5","tid":2270111,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />插撚到"},{"pid":"cdcba5b9737215dfd4cb509286918c416820f840","tid":2270111,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"美化/虛偽化叫「加強管治」<br />\n其實實為「加速侵略/毀滅」"},{"pid":"536d0074bdcd14aca2bb77fef7ece1dc96ede91c","tid":2270111,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"直接廢除所有關口<br />\n建立一小時港珠澳生活圈 真正大灣區啦<br />\n再加埋廢除廣東話 全面使用普通話<br />\n然後就係只用人民幣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc8a9a3f5de57e7d9f1f61c10ff597022d0b9f8","tid":2270111,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:36:05.000Z","msg":"成日愛國愛國<br />\n支國式愛國純粹係建基於錢<br />\n有幾多錢收買香港人？<br />\n無就咪講愛國啦"},{"pid":"10edf78bd75cf4c38f26993eb2e98370436537a4","tid":2270111,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"坦克碌港豬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72db1d75ff4d30c27589895bb113a2eee49352c","tid":2270111,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"堅決支持設立深圳市香港區<br />\n一勞永逸"},{"pid":"a7f577b7d53ef674d461321513886e93ba87322d","tid":2270111,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"預咗攬炒"},{"pid":"4b5df7f307a22a303ad773d79142b1a673b98b0f","tid":2270111,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:44:04.000Z","msg":"何君堯斥政府只懂委任英國法官<br />\n對賀知義任命投棄權票的何君堯認為，委任海外法官尚有10多個名額，香港應將眼界擴闊，大可委任東南亞、南非等地區的法官，來港擔任終院非常任法官，他呼籲政府勿把所有蛋放在一個籃子中，只懂委任英國法官：「你有冇考慮南非、印度、汶萊、新加坡、馬來西亞，新加坡，你睇人哋水平低，你望吓自己塊鏡，睇吓你有幾高啦&hellip;&hellip;新加坡、馬來西亞同我哋咁近，一個（委任海外法官）都冇？30個位（委任法官限額）一個都唔夠能夠容納得到？」梁美芬亦和應反問，星馬兩地法官，「一個有份量都無？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/IEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FIEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcykPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d44eb0f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FIEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4%2F&h=7b94334a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/IEPD7RY4IZEITJONT7Z4HQLDN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早排班奴才咁樣講，睇得出佢哋真係唔覺得香港制度有咩特別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00840dbf98c2570719f01561e958980ff90fabde","tid":2270111,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"又話『全力支持一國兩制』?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n習維尼你條仆街仔又講過唔算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/brS2Wy1d/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FbrS2Wy1d%2Fimage.png&h=10eaa679&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}